sequenceDiagram
    participant MM as ModelMesh<br/>Payload Processor
    participant KS as KServe<br/>InferenceLogger
    participant TS as TrustyAI Service<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant Store as Storage Backend<br/>PVC / DB / MinIO
    participant Model as Model Endpoint<br/>gRPC/HTTP2
    participant Prom as Prometheus<br/>HTTP Scrape
    participant User as User / Dashboard

    rect rgb(230, 245, 255)
        Note over MM,Store: Flow 1: ModelMesh Inference Payload Ingestion
        MM->>TS: POST /consumer/kserve/v2<br/>HTTP 80/TCP, No Auth
        TS->>Store: Persist inference data<br/>PVC (local) / JDBC 3306/TCP / HTTP 9000/TCP
    end

    rect rgb(230, 255, 230)
        Note over KS,Store: Flow 2: KServe CloudEvent Ingestion
        KS->>TS: HTTP CloudEvent (Knative Funqy)<br/>80/TCP, No Auth
        Note right of KS: org.kubeflow.serving.inference.request<br/>org.kubeflow.serving.inference.response
        TS->>Store: Persist inference data<br/>PVC / JDBC / HTTP
    end

    rect rgb(255, 245, 230)
        Note over TS,Prom: Flow 3: Scheduled Metric Calculation & Prometheus Scrape
        Note over TS: Quarkus Scheduler triggers<br/>periodic metric calculation
        TS->>Store: Read inference data
        Store-->>TS: Historical payloads
        Note over TS: Calculate SPD, DIR,<br/>drift metrics
        Prom->>TS: GET /q/metrics<br/>HTTP 80/TCP<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (SA)
        TS-->>Prom: trustyai_spd, trustyai_dir,<br/>drift metrics (Prometheus format)
    end

    rect rgb(255, 230, 230)
        Note over User,Model: Flow 4: Explainability Request (disabled in RHOAI)
        User->>TS: POST /explainers/local/lime<br/>HTTP 80/TCP, No Auth
        TS->>Store: Load inference data
        Store-->>TS: Training data
        loop Multiple inference calls
            TS->>Model: gRPC KServe v2 inference<br/>GRPCInferenceService<br/>HTTP2, No Auth
            Model-->>TS: Inference response
        end
        TS-->>User: Explanation result (JSON)<br/>HTTP 80/TCP
    end

    rect rgb(245, 230, 255)
        Note over User,TS: Flow 5: Fairness Metric Request (on-demand)
        User->>TS: POST /metrics/group/fairness/spd<br/>HTTP 80/TCP, No Auth
        TS->>Store: Read inference data
        Store-->>TS: Historical payloads
        Note over TS: Calculate SPD metric
        TS-->>User: SPD result + schedule<br/>metric for periodic calc
    end
